---
import TechStack from './TechStack.astro';
---

<section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 antialiased">
    <div class="py-16 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl sm:py-24 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md text-center mb-12 lg:mb-16">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">I miei servizi</h2>
            <p class="font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:text-xl">Mi concentro su soluzioni web innovative e di qualità che garantiscono risultati concreti per la tua attività.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 md:gap-12 md:space-y-0">
            <div class="group p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-6 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 lg:h-16 lg:w-16 dark:bg-blue-900/30 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:dark:bg-blue-600 group-hover:shadow-blue-500/50 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 lg:w-8 lg:h-8 dark:text-blue-300 group-hover:text-white group-hover:dark:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m8 8-4 4 4 4m8 0 4-4-4-4m-2-3-4 14"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white">Web Development</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Creo siti e applicazioni web performanti e scalabili, utilizzando tecnologie moderne per trasformare idee in realtà.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-6 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-100 lg:h-16 lg:w-16 dark:bg-purple-900/30 group-hover:bg-purple-600 group-hover:dark:bg-purple-600 group-hover:shadow-purple-500/50 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 lg:w-8 lg:h-8 dark:text-purple-300 group-hover:text-white group-hover:dark:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.005 10.19a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v.233l5.998 3.464L18 11.423v-.232a1 1 0 1 1 2 0V12a1 1 0 0 1-.5.866l-6.997 4.042a1 1 0 0 1-1 0l-6.998-4.042a1 1 0 0 1-.5-.866v-.81a1 1 0 0 1 1-1ZM5 15.15a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v.232l5.997 3.464 5.998-3.464v-.232a1 1 0 1 1 2 0v.81a1 1 0 0 1-.5.865l-6.998 4.042a1 1 0 0 1-1 0L4.5 17.824a1 1 0 0 1-.5-.866v-.81a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/><path d="M12.503 2.134a1 1 0 0 0-1 0L4.501 6.17A1 1 0 0 0 4.5 7.902l7.002 4.047a1 1 0 0 0 1 0l6.998-4.04a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.732l-6.997-4.042Z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white">UI/UX Design</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Progetto interfacce intuitive, con particolare attenzione all'esperienza utente, all'accessibilità e al responsive design.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-6 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-100 lg:h-16 lg:w-16 dark:bg-green-900/30 group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:dark:bg-green-600 group-hover:shadow-green-500/50 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 lg:w-8 lg:h-8 dark:text-green-300 group-hover:text-white group-hover:dark:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4.5V19a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h15M7 14l4-4 4 4 5-5m0 0h-3.207M20 9v3.207"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white">SEO & Best Practices</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Ottimizzo ogni pagina secondo le migliori pratiche SEO per migliorare la performance e l'accessibilità.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <TechStack/>
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <a href="#contatti" class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500 hover:underline">
                Scopri come posso aiutare la tua attività
                <svg class="ml-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
